title: Tested in 2017: Sean's Favorite Things!
description:
Our 3D printer expert Sean's favorite things of the past year include a modelmaking guide book, earbuds, custom LEGO minifigs, a handy driver, and a sculpt he found at a convention this year. Plus, an MP3 player pick!

RSP SM 03 book
https://www.rinaldistudiopress.com/

Cowon Plenue D
https://www.amazon.com/Cowon-Plenue-Resolution-Music-Player/dp/B01A8NU5CG/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1513297952&sr=8-1&keywords=plenue+d

Zero Audio phones
https://www.amazon.com/AUDIO-ear-stereo-headphone-carbo-ZH-DX210-CB/dp/B0093VVPM4/ref=sr_1_cc_1?s=aps&ie=UTF8&qid=1513298086&sr=1-1-catcorr&keywords=zero+audio+basso

Wiha Ultra Driver
https://www.amazon.com/Wiha-77792-Industrial-Ultra-Driver/dp/B01MRETJFN/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&qid=1513298167&sr=8-3&keywords=wiha+ultra+driver

Custom LEGO minifigs
http://www.wallercustoms.com/

Space Kook
http://apsculpturestudio.com/

Shot by Gunther Kirsch
Edited by Norman Chan

Subscribe for more videos! http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=testedcom
